title: Starting a fun youtube channel, looking for friend to join! (G5)
body:
Hi everyone, 

I am starting a youtube channel for creating fun league of legends content.
Going to be consistent and looking for someone who would just like to have fun, suggest crazy ideas from time to time, climb seriously, etc!

Join my discord! https://discord.gg/GFwsza
Add me in-game! Slyxia OwO

Looking forward to meeting you!

replies.body: I'll join! Sounds like great fun!
